o\": 1500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The loss proved more heartbreaking as Marcial temporarily set his professional career aside, hoping to deliver the Philippines' first gold medal in Olympic boxing.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1628, \"end\": 1639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9998801430560899, \"rank\": 0.0001182443696855862, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The loss\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"Marcial\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"his professional career\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1598}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic boxing\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marcial last fought professionally in March, battering Thailand's Thoedsak Sinam in a knockout win, before he turned his focus on the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1733, \"end\": 1741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_under-23_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9980495512000136, \"rank\": 0.0015597679699634306, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_under-23_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_under-23_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marcial\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1721}, {\"ngram\": \"a knockout win\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"his focus\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He trained in the United States then joined the national boxing team in its training camps in Metz, France, and in Saarbrucken, Germany.\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\":